						<p><hi rend="bold">King: ⎯⎯ Year: <hi rend="italic">Śōbhakrit, Kārttika</hi> śu. di. 2, Monday.</hi></p>						

						<p>In characters of the 15th century A.D. It registers the gift of taxes collected from the artisans <hi rend="italic">kamsāli</hi> and <hi rend="italic">Kammari</hi> of the village Juttāḍa to the god Vallabharāya of the same village by Vallaya-Paḍalu-Mahāpātra, a friend of Vallabharājumahāpātrā the chief of Vōḍādi.</p>						

